{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/library_header.png?t=1738301491\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A casual fish-raising simulation game &quot;Idle Aquarium&quot; is conveniently displayed on your screen, allowing you to enjoy the joy of being a fish keeper while working.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/54901e27f7004213fbd4f528300ffba2.mp4_20241225_032913.gif?t=1738301491\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Feed Your Fish:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Feed your little fish, make friends with them, unlock new species, and even some very rare ones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/54901e27f7004213fbd4f528300ffba2.mp4_20241225_033344.gif?t=1738301491\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Decorate Your Aquarium:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Decorate your aquarium and turn your desktop into your favorite style, with a variety of decorations to meet all your needs. Whether it's a planted tank or a South American tank, any style you want is possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/54901e27f7004213fbd4f528300ffba2.mp4_20241225_032929.gif?t=1738301491\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multitasking Capability:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Comfortably placed at the bottom of the screen, you can take care of your fish while accomplishing other tasks. Or switch to &quot;Focus Mode&quot; to quietly enjoy them without much interaction.A casual fish-raising simulation game &quot;Idle Aquarium&quot; is conveniently displayed on your screen, allowing you to enjoy the fun of being a fish keeper while worki